      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_impact-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "成宮すず！　{user}さんの\n呼び出しに応じて、来てあげましたわよ！",
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……相変わらず元気だな\n忙しい中、来てもらってすまない",
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "他ならぬ{user}さんの呼び出しですもの\nそれに、打ち合わせも仕事のうちです。お気になさらず",
      "startTime": 14.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、私に直接話したいことってなんですの？",
      "startTime": 19.4149431069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、仕事の話なんだけど……今までと違うタイプの\n仕事だから、直接説明した方がいいと思って",
      "startTime": 28.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "今までと違うお仕事、ですって？\n……ふっ、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私はもう駆け出しの新人アイドルでは\nありませんわよ？",
      "startTime": 41.9419503212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロを背負って立つ『二代目星降る奇跡』\nこの成宮すずに、そんな気遣いは無用ですわ",
      "startTime": 47.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "どんな仕事でも余裕でこなしてご覧に入れます",
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、なら良かった。あのな、実は……\nすずに連続テレビドラマの出演オファーがきたんだ",
      "startTime": 60.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、やっぱり私の想定内のお仕事ですわ\n――って連ドラの出演！？",
      "startTime": 69.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、人気ドラマで、確か今シーズン10が放送中だ\n毎回殺人事件が起きるんだよな。すずも知ってるだろ？",
      "startTime": 77.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "それ、子供の頃から観ていますわ！\nわっ、わっ、私が出演……！？",
      "startTime": 86.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ぜ、全国放送の有名連ドラ……\nしかも私が好きなあの作品で、女優デビュー！",
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すず、大丈夫か？　震えてるぞ？",
      "startTime": 100.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、震えてませんわ！　さ、さすがにほんのちょっと\nわずかばかり、お、驚きましたけど！",
      "startTime": 108.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "役者の仕事は今回が初めてだけど、新しいファンを\n獲得出来るし、今後の活動の幅も広がると思う",
      "startTime": 115.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でもまずは、すずの意向を聞きたい\n興味はあるか？",
      "startTime": 122.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……。ついに演技の世界にも\n私の才能が伝わってしまったのですわね……",
      "startTime": 127.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、日本のドラマの発展のため\n女優としてお力を貸したいのはやまやまなのですが……",
      "startTime": 135.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "私、成宮すずは、麻奈様の後を継ぐ\n天才アイドルを目指す身",
      "startTime": 144.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルと女優との二足のわらじを履くべきでしょうか\nまだ時期尚早な気もしますわ……はぁ、悩ましい",
      "startTime": 152.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……そういうことならすずの気持ちを尊重するよ",
      "startTime": 159.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "ですけど、{user}さんが\nど～～してもと言うことでしたら……",
      "startTime": 166.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "残念だけど、今回は見送ろう",
      "startTime": 170.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "ちょーーっとお待ちなさい！！\n諦めるのが早過ぎません！？",
      "startTime": 175.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し熱心に説得したら、渋々\n「そんなに頼むなら仕方ありませんわね～」",
      "startTime": 181.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "――と折れるかもしれませんのに！",
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、ドラマに出たいのか？",
      "startTime": 188.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "出たいですわ！\nそんなに頼むなら仕方ないですわ！",
      "startTime": 194.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "言ってることがめちゃくちゃだぞ……\nまぁ、いい。それですずの役なんだけど……",
      "startTime": 199.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、成宮すず、ついに女優デビュー！\nこれで、私の魅力を新しいファンに届けられますわ！",
      "startTime": 208.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、すず、俺の話、聞いてるか？",
      "startTime": 213.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.333333399997,
          "startTime": 215.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "こうしてはいられません\n早く月ストのメンバーに連絡を……",
      "startTime": 219.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、優のお母様は有名な女優さんでしたわね\nぜひ演技指導をお願いしましょう！",
      "startTime": 227.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "すず、ちょっと待ってくれ\nまずは脚本を読んで――",
      "startTime": 231.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
